g shut.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Please enter your information using the form at <a href="https://www.turtlebeach.com/contactsupport" class=""><u>https://www.turtlebeach.com/contactsupport</u></a> to participate in the voluntary recall.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">If your unit is affected, we will send you a pre-paid shipping label to return the recalled headset directly to Turtle Beach. Please do not return the recalled headset to the place of purchase.</span><br></li><li><span style="font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">When we receive your recalled headset, we expect to be able to ship you a free replacement headset within 10-14 business days.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">If you have additional questions, you can call Turtle Beach toll-free at 855-868-4832 from 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. ET Monday through Friday.</span></li></ul><p></p></div></div></article></div></section></section></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1579128705953" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-4" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1579128705953" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="4px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-4" id="c-1579128705969" data-id="1579128705969" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" id="e-1579128739151" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1" data-id="1579128739151"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/55e51c00-f2c1-4a1a-aa71-36ca639b37dd/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="xo four headset earcup" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-4" id="c-1579128725914" data-id="1579128725914" styl